SUMMARY:Monthly Cuban Salsa Party
DESCRIPTION:RCR hosts a Cuban Dance Party every 1st Saturday of the month at the LMDC in Oakland. Classes and social. \nAt all of our monthly parties we celebrate the birthdays of everyone born in that month. \nThe Lake Merritt Dance Center is a PERFECT venue for dancing\, featuring a smooth vintage hardwood dance floor with ample space to dance. \nVisit the Rueda Con Ritmo Events page for further details.
