SUMMARY:Latin Dance Class & St Pete Pier Salsa Dance Party!
DESCRIPTION:Latin Dance Class & St Pete Pier Salsa Dance Party!\n\n\n🌟 Experience the Magic: Monthly Social Dance at Pier Plaza! 🌟 \n  \nJoin the RELPro Dance Promotions family for our beloved monthly social! Imagine dancing under the evening lights\, with the gentle breeze and breathtaking views of the water at the Pier Plaza. This isn’t just a dance; it’s an experience! \n  \nWe love supporting our local talent\, which is why every month we bring in a fantastic local dance school to teach an engaging Latin Dance Class at the beginning of the event. It’s the perfect way to warm up\, learn something new\, and connect before the social dancing begins! \n  \nCome for the Class\, Stay for the Social! \n  \nFun Latin Dance Class: $5 Recommended Donation (starts at 6:00 PM) \n  \nVibrant Pop-up Social: $5 Recommended Donation (continues after class!) \n  \nYour generous donations help us keep these incredible community events going! \n  \nWhat’s your dance anthem? Send us your music requests and let’s create the perfect playlist together! \n  \n#RELProVibes #PierPlazaSocial #StPeteDanceScene #LatinMusic #DanceConnect #CommunityEvent #SupportLocalArtists #DanceAllNight #WaterfrontViews
URL:https://golatindance.com/event/latin-dance-class-st-pete-pier-salsa-dance-party/2026-03-07/
LOCATION:St. Petersburg Pier
CATEGORIES:Tampa
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://golatindance.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/295075_image.png
END:VEVENT
