SUMMARY:J&L Underground
DESCRIPTION:EACH 1ST SATURDAY OF THE MONTH\nJ&L Underground Social will be bringing you a night of energy\, fun\, and the best mix of Bachata (with some sprinkles of Kizomba\, Salsa\, and Merengue ) to keep you dancing all night!\nLocation: Rumba y Timbal Studio\, 7 Temple Street\, Cambridge (YWCA)\nClass Workshop:\n7pm-8pm\nBachata Footwork Challenge (modified for all levels) OR Bachata for Beginners Crash Course\n8pm-11pm\nSocial Dancing (80% Bachata\, 20% Salsa/Merengue)\nCost:\n$15 (includes J&L Footwork Challenge Class)\nMusic: DJ Lui-G\nParking: Street Parking and Nearby Parking Lots or Central Square T Stop\nCan’t wait to bring that island feel to Boston! See you on the dancefloor!
URL:https://golatindance.com/event/jl-underground-social-2/2026-03-07/
LOCATION:Rumba Y Timbal Dance Studio\, 7 Temple St\, Cambridge\, MA\, 02139\, United States
CATEGORIES:Boston
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://golatindance.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Screenshot-2026-02-06-100756.png
