SUMMARY:Rhythm House Multi-Genre Social
DESCRIPTION:Don’t miss out on the multi- genre dance social\, bringing to you the greatest in Salsa\, West Coast Swing\, Bachata\, and many more! Don’t see your style on here? Send us a message so we can include it! This is NOT YOUR AVERAGE SOCIAL! It’s a place to grab some beers and pizza with your friends and dance to some of your favorite music. FRIENDLY TO DANCERS AND NON-DANCERS alike.
