SUMMARY:Salsa + Bachata Saturdays
DESCRIPTION:💃 Mark your calendars for EVERY 1ST SATURDAY! \nVeDanza Entertainment’s Salsa Bachata Saturdays at Dr. Boochart is the perfect way to kick off each month! 🕺 \nStart with a beginner-friendly class by Patrick & Cynthia from 7:30-8:30pm\, then dance the night away until midnight with the incredible beats from our resident DJ OROD! \nNo experience needed – just bring your energy and let the rhythm guide you! Located at 105 E Grand Ave\, Escondido. \nTag your dance partner below! Who’s joining us this month? \n#VeDanzaSaturdays #SalsaNight #BachataLife #EscondidoNightlife #DrBootlegger #DanceTheNightAway
URL:https://golatindance.com/event/salsa-bachata-saturdays/2026-03-07/
LOCATION:Dr. Boochart\, 105 E. Grand Ave\, Escondido\, CA\, 92025\, United States
CATEGORIES:San Diego
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://golatindance.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/484051138_1253086193489956_4540444027531400369_n.jpg
