DESCRIPTION:Teteo is back baby!! The ONLY Dominican party in Denver!! Here con to’ el flow!! Get ready for a night full of the best Latin flavor!! LFG!\n\n\nWe are back once again with another top tier artist for YOU!  \n \nMile high city welcomes Eda Kachiri back to Denver! Bringing you 2 amazing classes\, followed by a night of dancing 💃 to the best salsa\, bachata\, merengue\, and reggaeton!! 🎶  \n \n📆 Saturday March 7  \n📍 ELEMENTAL STUDIOS  \n4668 Glencoe St.  \nDenver\, Co \n \n7pm: Tradicional bachata ladies styling.  \n8pm: Traditional bachata partner work.  \n9pm-12am: Social dancing  \nDJ Juan Bachata \n \nEarly Bird Pricing: (Eventbrite link above)  \n1 class + social = $25 \n2 class + social = $40  \nSocial only: $15  \n \n*****PRICE INCREASE AT THE DOOR******
URL:https://golatindance.com/event/vamos-pal-teteo-con-eda-kachiri/
LOCATION:Elemental Studios\, 4668 Glencoe Street\, Denver\, CO 80216\, Denver\, CO\, 80216\, US
CATEGORIES:Denver
