SUMMARY:Sydney SALSA Marathon
DESCRIPTION:SALSA SOCIAL….. keeping you DANCING from 2006 – 2026! \nHave you been to our NEW AMAZING VENUE? Its SO much more than just a dance venue!! 250+ monthly dancers can’t be wrong! \nTHE POLISH CLUB\, Ashfield:\n– Main road entrance: 182 Liverpool Rd ASHFIELD next to Cruise Cafe.\n– FREE onsite underground Parking at rear of venue via NORTON St Ashfield.\n– ASHFIELD Train station 7 min walk.\n– All Bus routes via LIVERPOOL RD ASHFIELD.\nSydney’s ORIGINAL Monthly Salsa Party returns\, with HOURS of NON STOP DANCING!! \nSALSA SOCIAL MARATHON @ The POLISH CLUB:\n– Recently completed BRAND NEW BUILDING!\n– HUGE completely WOODEN FLOOR venue space!\n– 4 metre ceilings\n– Aircon\n– Main road entry: 182 Liverpool Rd. Ashfield\n– Car Park entry: 73 Norton Street\, Ashfield (70 secured car spaces)\n– Multi story carpark 50m away (Coles 11pm close).\n– Ashfield Train station 7 min walk.\n– All Bus routes via Liverpool Rd Ashfield\n– Lots of free on street parking.\n– Great bar in party room.\n– Separate seated breakout area.\n– Great bar food & bar by breakout area.\n– Restaurant.\n– Private restaurant function room.\n– Coffee shop with polish snacks / sandwiches til LATE 12am (yes til midnight)\n– Become a member ($5) & save on every food\, drinks\, snack & coffee purchases!! \nSYDNEY SALSA MARATHON EVENING SCHEDULE:\n– 7pm: 3 x FREE Salsa Classes to chose from 7pm (inc in cover charge)\n– 8pm: NON STOP SOCIAL DANCING til LAAAATE!\n– 3 DJ’S Resident DJ’s Chris\, Gav + Mambo-G playing the very best in NYC flavoured Salsa\, Mambo\, Cha cha\, & a touch of Bachata \nCome early or come late\, just come & dance your socks off!\nCLUB entry $25 CASH (PREFERRED)\, $26 (card payment)\nincludes a choice of 3 complimentary Salsa classes 7pm (Beg\, Int\, Adv). \nEVERYONE welcome from beginner to professionals.\nCome & enjoy another legendary night of Music & Dance!\nSPREAD THE WORD BAILADORES LET’S PARTY at THE BEST SALSA VENUE in SYDNEY!! \nSee you there! \nMambo-G & the Sydney Salsa Marathon Team
URL:https://golatindance.com/event/sydney-salsa-marathon-march-7th-polish-club-ashfield/
LOCATION:182 Liverpool Rd\, 182 Liverpool Rd\, Ashfield\, NSW\, 2131\, Australia
CATEGORIES:Sydney
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://golatindance.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/636715366_10164671759098524_2059002448433218993_n.jpg
ORGANIZER;CN="Graeme Haney":MAILTO:houseofmambo@gmail_com
END:VEVENT
