SUMMARY:PARTY PA' TI!
DESCRIPTION:🔥 Get ready for 𝗣𝗮𝗿𝘁𝘆 𝗣𝗮’ 𝗧𝗶! — London’s monthly Salsa & Bachata night brought to you by Salsateca & BOS! Taking place every first Saturday of the month\, this event offers: \n💃 2 rooms – one for Salsa & one for Bachata\n🎓 4 levels of lessons – Absolute Beginner to Advanced\n🎧 Top DJs\n🎶 A unique mix of Cuban\, Puerto Rican\, Modern & Sensual Latin beats \n⸻ \n🕒 SCHEDULE \n7:00 PM – Doors Open\n7:30 PM – 9:30 PM – Salsa & Bachata Lessons:\n– Bachata Room:\n• 7:30 – 8:30 → Dominican Bachata (Levels 1\, 2\, & 3)\n• 8:30 – 9:30 → Sensual Bachata (Levels 1\, 2\, & 3) \n– Salsa Room:\n• 7:30 – 8:30 → Cross Body Salsa (Levels 1 & 3)\n• 8:30 – 9:30 → Cross Body Salsa (Levels 2 & 4) \n9:30 PM – 2:00 AM – Party Pa’ Ti Begins!\nDance the night away to the best of Salsa & Bachata in both rooms! \n📍 Guy’s Bar\, Boland House\, King’s College London\, SE1 9RT\n🚉 Just 1 min from London Bridge Station – Next to The Shard! \n⸻ \n🎟 PRICES\n💃 Lessons + Party:\n• £16 (Early Bird) | £18 (In Advance) | £20 (At the Door)\n🕺 Party Only:\n• £12 (Early Bird) | £13 (In Advance) | £15 (At the Door) \n*Limited Numbers for Early Bird! Get in Quick! \n⸻ \nWhether you’re a complete beginner or a seasoned dancer\, Party Pa’ Ti is the perfect way to learn\, dance\, and meet new people in a vibrant\, friendly setting. Come solo or with a partner — everyone is welcome!
URL:https://golatindance.com/event/party-pa-ti-launch-party/2026-03-07/
LOCATION:Guy’s Bar\, Boland House\, St Thomas St\, London\, SE1 9RT\, United Kingdom
CATEGORIES:London
END:VEVENT
