SUMMARY:Sensual Saturday Carnival Themed Party!
DESCRIPTION:Let’s celebrate Carnival!\n\n\nSENSUAL SATURDAY CARNIVAL THEMED PARTY! \nLet’s celebrate Carnival! \nSamba Carnival and Salsa Performances by Moves n’ Vibes and Fleure! \nBAD BUNNY SUPER BOWL CHOREO CHALLENGE NUEVO YORK \nLearn the original Super Bowl salsa choreography to “NuevaYo” by Bad Bunny. Fierce. Sharp. Grounded. Full of attitude. Perform it live at the social that night! \nSchedule: \n• 7:45pm to 9pm: Bad Bunny SuperBowl Choreo Challenge “NuevaYo” with Nina \n• 9pm to 10pm: Sensual Bachata Workshop with Inna \n• 10pm to 1am: Social with DJ Ceijay spinning the best Bachata\, Salsa\, Kizomba & Zouk! \nCover: \n$30 for two workshops and social (in advance)$25 for one workshop and social (in advance)$20 for social only \n**Register in advance and receive the salsa choreo counts in advance! \nPayment options: Eventbrite\, Cash\, Venmo (@inna-grant)\, PayPal\, CashApp\, Credit Card \nLocation: 44 5th Street\, Cambridge\, MA 02141 \nParking: FREE Street Parking \nNo partner needed—just bring your energy! \nCome dance\, connect\, and celebrate! \n \n#SensualSaturday #Bachata #Salsa #LatinDance #CambridgeEvents #MovesnVibes #DanceCommunity #LiveMusic #Brazil #Carnival
URL:https://golatindance.com/event/sensual-saturday-carnival-themed-party/
LOCATION:Moves & Vibes Dancing Academy\, 44 5th Street\, Cambridge\, MA 02141\, Cambridge\, MA\, 02141\, US
CATEGORIES:Boston
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://golatindance.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/302954_image.jpg
END:VEVENT
